Project Idea

To-do list that algorithmically suggests a project to complete based on the amount of time you currently have available, the rated importance of the items in the to-do list, the approaching deadlines for each item (if any), and your current location.

recurring tasks

"ask later?"  some settings such as deadlines, enter address where task needs to be completed,  

gameification: trophies and achievements - 5 items completed rated very important!, etc. streaks. 

goals - setting and categorizing goals - short term, long term, urgent, new year's resolutions,

